QUESTION:
A palindrome word is a sequence of characters which reads the same backward as forward, such as madam, racecar.
Define a JS function whether a word is palindrome or not.

(function(word) {
  word == word.split('').reverse().join('') ? alert(`${word} is a palindrome`) : alert(`${word} is not palindrome\nTry again!`)
})(prompt('please enter a word'))
